        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <title>GENERAL</title>
                <para>The Spicer 14 Inch Solo clutch is a pull type clutch specifically engineered for Class 6 and 7
                    medium duty trucks with flat-flywheel diesel engines.
                </para>
                <para>The Solo clutch is available with ceramic 8 spring dampened driven discs and greaseable release
                    bearing only. Options include 1-1/2 inch, 1-3/4 inch and 2 inch spline, single or two driven disc
                    assemblies, and capacity to handle engines up to 900 ft-lbs. of torque.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
